14:
From the descendants of Levi who returned to Judah there was: Shemaiah son of Hasshub;\li2 Hasshub son of Azrikam;
\li2 Azrikam son of Hashabiah;
\li2 Hashabiah was a descendant of Levi's youngest son Merari.
\li1

15:
Other descendants of Levi who returned to Judah were: Bakbakkar, Heresh, Galal, and Mattaniah son of Mika;\li2 Mika son of Zicri;
\li2 Zicri son of Asaph;
\li1

16:
There was also Obadiah son of Shemaiah;\li2 Shemaiah son of Galal;
\li2 Galal son of Jeduthun;
\li1 There was also Berekiah son of Asa;
\li2 Asa son of Elkanah, who lived in one of the villages where the Netophath people lived.


